flowchart LR
    M["/mount your folder"] --> A["/analyse"]
    A --> S1[.docs/ markdown mirror]
    A --> S2[.analyse/ artifacts]
    S1 & S2 --> R{you review}
    R -->|looks good| P["/publishdocs"]
    P --> F[(your real folder)]
    R -.->|not yet| X[nothing is written]
    style F fill:#dfd
    style X fill:#fdd
